Name: Earth Form
Functional Text: When this hits, create an Embodiment of Earth token.

Name: Lightning Form
Functional Text: When this hits, create an Embodiment of Lightning token.

Name: Zen State
Functional Text:
This enters the arena with a balance counter. At the beginning of your action phase, destroy this unless you remove a balance counter from it.

If you would be dealt damage, prevent 1 of that damage.
